message.body: Just went to a party and met a dude named Ben who did a dissertation boot camp with you. He's dissertations for the second year and is in French lit.
I said your name then said tall pretty British outrageous fabulous clothes and it clicked. My next clue would have been eyeliner. xxxxxxxxxxxxx
Oh yeah, he's a nice guy. I'm sorry boys are bad! We should go eat ice cream and discuss at some point soon, yes?
